

'''= Use of organic waste to promote composting, education and citizenship.'''

URL: https://www.facebook.com/revolucao.dosbaldinhos/info


=Description=


This local initiative of management of organic waste contributes to reduce the number of rats in the slums of Chico Mendes e Novo  Horizonte, in  Florianópolis (SC); promotes the use of organic waste for composting, urban agriculture, education and citizenship.


